{{Infobox hospital | name = National Hospital'''National Hospital''' | org/group = | logo = | logo_size = | image = | image_size = 225 | alt = | caption = | coordinates = <!-- {{coord|LAT|LON|type:landmark|display=inline, title}} --> | location = [[Niamey]], [[Niger]] | region = | state = | country = | healthcare = <!-- UK: NHS; AU/CA: Medicare; ELSE free-form text, e.g. Private --> | funding = | type = | affiliation = | patron = | network = | standards = | emergency = Yes | beds = 244 beds.<ref>[http://www.endfistula.org/download/niger_factsheet.pdf Niger Factsheet] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090106212416/http://www.endfistula.org/download/niger_factsheet.pdf |date=2009-01-06 }} EndFistula.org</ref> | speciality = | helipad = No | h1-number = | h1-length-f = | h1-length-m = | h1-surface = <!-- up to h12 --> | founded = 1922 | closed = | demolished = | website = <!-- {{URL|www.example.com}} --> | other_links = | module = }}
The '''National Hospital''' is a hospital in [[Niamey]], [[Niger]]. It has 244 beds.<ref>[http://www.endfistula.org/download/niger_factsheet.pdf Niger Factsheet] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090106212416/http://www.endfistula.org/download/niger_factsheet.pdf |date=2009-01-06 }} EndFistula.org</ref> The hospital was founded in 1922.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.globalhand.org/en/browse/regions/africa/all/organisation/21706|title=Hopital National de Niger|last=|first=|date=|website=Crossroads Global Hanf|archive-url=http://archive.fo/6YHHF|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref>
== Services == The hospital provides a wide range of services to residents of Niamey and the greater region. As of September, 2018 the National Hospital has two [[Otorhinolaryngology|Otolaryngologists]], two [[Ophthalmology|Ophthalmologists]], five [[Radiology|Radiologists]], three [[Cardiology|Cardiologists]], three [[Dermatology|Dermatologists]], four [[Obstetrics and gynaecology|Obsetricians/Gynecologist]]<nowiki/>s, five [[Dentist|dentists]] and one [[psychiatrist]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ne.usembassy.gov/u-s-citizen-services/local-resources-of-u-s-citizens/doctors/|title=Medical Assistance|last=|first=|date=|website=US Embassy in Niger|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref>
